From 362e51c82497404dafff61ebc736f6fc2cb844a8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Mar 2026 07:43:57 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Update frontend for new Supabase schema: products, order
 lines, team, emails in company/contact views

- Add OdooProduct, OdooOrderLine, OdooUser types + new columns on Company, Email, Contact
- Company detail: use get_company_full_context RPC, add Emails/Productos/Operaciones tabs
  with payment behavior, aging, pending deliveries, recent sales/invoices/payments
- Contact detail: use get_contact_communications RPC, show threads and KG relationships
- Dashboard: add Team section via get_team_dashboard RPC with pending/overdue counts
- System: add row counts for odoo_products, odoo_order_lines, odoo_users tables

https://claude.ai/code/session_01BtXt1qaYc7Y4n2imU2FWQX
